  combo: 74
  dialogue:
  - 'That mouse sea captain looks scary! '
  - "Fear not, little ones. The Captain is a respectable man and wouldn\u2019t draw
    weapons in front of children. "
  - "Little ones? We\u2019re quite tall for an adult!  "
  - "(She looks her companion up and down before giving them a look) \u2026 I see."
  names:
  - '"Gerald"'
  - Potion Pixies
